data.description: Discover this hidden gem, a 3-bedroom, 2-bath home ideally located in close proximity to Altus Air Force Base and a charming neighborhood small park area. This property showcases nice landscaping with new sprinklers, double driveways, and an exclusive RV parking area within a fenced yard, complete with an electric door and key fob access. Inside, you'll find a living space with recently installed new tile. Make this home yours and experience the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, with a neighborhood park just a few blocks away for outdoor enjoyment!"
